---
// About Component - Personal introduction section
---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header fade-up">
      <span class="section-tag">关于我</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="gradient-text">你好，我是钱磊</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-image fade-up stagger-1">
        <div class="image-wrapper">
          <div class="image-placeholder">
            <span class="avatar-text">L</span>
          </div>
          <div class="image-glow"></div>
          <div class="image-ring"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="floating-icons">
          <div class="icon-bubble icon-1">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
              <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-bubble icon-2">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"></line>
              <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="icon-bubble icon-3">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-text fade-up stagger-2">
        <p class="about-intro">
          我是一名充满热情的<strong>前端开发者</strong>和<strong>自由开发者</strong>，
          专注于创建令人惊艳的数字体验。
        </p>
        
        <p>
          毕业于上海大学，曾就职于IBM大中华地区担任技术顾问。
          多年的开发经验让我深谙用户体验的重要性，
          我相信代码不仅仅是功能的实现，更是艺术与逻辑的完美结合。
        </p>
        
        <p>
          我热爱探索新技术，追求代码的优雅和简洁。
          无论是构建复杂的Web应用，还是打造精致的交互动画，
          我都力求在每个细节上做到极致。
        </p>
        
        <div class="about-highlights">
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>现代化前端技术栈</span>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>用户体验优先</span>
          </div>
          <div class="highlight-item">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>持续学习与创新</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="/dist/index.html" class="btn btn-secondary about-cta">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
          查看完整简历
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-color), transparent);
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }
  
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 280px;
    height: 280px;
  }
  
  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  
  .avatar-text {
    font-size: 6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .image-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20px;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(40px);
    opacity: 0.4;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: pulse-glow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .image-ring {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -15px;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: spin-slow 20s linear infinite;
  }
  
  .floating-icons {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -30px;
  }
  
  .icon-bubble {
    position: absolute;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }
  
  .icon-1 {
    top: 10%;
    right: -10%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }
  
  .icon-2 {
    bottom: 15%;
    left: -15%;
    animation-delay: -2s;
  }
  
  .icon-3 {
    bottom: 5%;
    right: -5%;
    animation-delay: -4s;
  }
  
  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .about-intro {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .about-intro strong {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .about-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  
  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  .highlight-item svg {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .about-cta {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .about-image {
      order: -1;
    }
    
    .about-highlights {
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .about-cta {
      align-self: center;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .image-wrapper {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }
    
    .avatar-text {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
    
    .floating-icons {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
